  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个完整的FinTech支付系统认证流程图。核心有三个参与者：Web客户端、Keycloak授权服务器，还有Synapse消息服务器。Web客户端代表FinTech_PaymentGateway，Keycloak那边有两个不同的client注册：一个是给Synapse用的FinTech_AuthVault，另一个是给Web客户端用的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Web Client (FinTech_PaymentGateway)",
        "Keycloak",
        "Synapse Server",
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "client_id",
        "client_secret"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以Synapse和Web客户端都要先在Keycloak注册，但Synapse用的是机密客户端模式，需要client_secret，而Web客户端只需要client_id？另外Web客户端的注册名称是FinTech_AuthVault还是FinTech_PaymentGateway？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Web Client (FinTech_PaymentGateway)",
        "Keycloak",
        "Synapse Server",
        "client_id",
        "client_secret",
        "FinTech_AuthVault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "对，Synapse是confidential client，需要client_secret。Web客户端在Keycloak注册的client_id是FinTech_AuthVault，但它本身代表的业务实体是FinTech_PaymentGateway。另外Web客户端发起token请求的时候，会带上FinTech_TransactionQueue这个标识。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Web Client (FinTech_PaymentGateway)",
        "Keycloak",
        "Synapse Server",
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "client_secret"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把三个参与者和初始注册步骤画出来。Web客户端和Synapse分别向Keycloak注册，Synapse带client_id和client_secret，Web客户端只带client_id。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Web Client (FinTech_PaymentGateway)",
        "Keycloak",
        "Synapse Server",
        "Register with client_id & client_secret",
        "Register with client_id (FinTech_AuthVault)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来是核心的认证流程。Web客户端走Authorization Code流程，带PKCE。第一步是向Keycloak发起授权码请求，Keycloak返回重定向带授权码，然后Web客户端用授权码换token，这里要标注FinTech_TransactionQueue。Keycloak返回access token和refresh token。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Web Client (FinTech_PaymentGateway)",
        "Keycloak",
        "Authorization Code Request",
        "Redirect with Auth Code",
        "Token Request (FinTech_TransactionQueue)",
        "Access & Refresh Tokens"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Web客户端的Authorization Code流程画好了，1到4步。然后Synapse也要获取token对吧？它用client credentials flow？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Web Client (FinTech_PaymentGateway)",
        "Keycloak",
        "Authorization Code Request",
        "Redirect with Auth Code",
        "Token Request (FinTech_TransactionQueue)",
        "Access & Refresh Tokens"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，Synapse作为服务器端，用confidential client credentials flow，直接向Keycloak发起token请求，标注FinTech_AuthVault，Keycloak只返回access token，不需要refresh token。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Synapse Server",
        "Keycloak",
        "Token Request (FinTech_AuthVault)",
        "Access Token"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Synapse的服务器认证画好了，第5、6步。接下来是API通信部分？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Synapse Server",
        "Keycloak",
        "Token Request (FinTech_AuthVault)",
        "Access Token",
        "API Communication"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，API通信是重点。Web客户端向Synapse发起API请求，带上access token。Synapse收到后要去Keycloak做token introspection验证，Keycloak返回验证结果，Synapse再返回API响应给Web客户端。这是第7到10步。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Web Client (FinTech_PaymentGateway)",
        "Synapse Server",
